{
  "mode_id": "MY_QUOTE",
  "display_name": "自定义语录",
  "icon": "my_quote",
  "cacheable": false,
  "description": "随机生成一条有力量的语录，或使用你输入的语录内容",
  "content": {
    "type": "llm_json",
    "prompt_template": "你是一位擅长写短句的格言作者。请输出一句简短有力量的语录（中英文均可），并给出作者署名（可虚构但要像真实作者名）。\n用 JSON 输出：\n{{\"quote\": \"语录（60字以内）\", \"author\": \"作者（20字以内，可留空）\"}}\n要求：\n1. 不要鸡汤泛泛之谈，要具体、克制、有锋芒\n2. 避免政治敏感与人身攻击\n3. 只输出 JSON，不要其他文字\n环境：{context}",
    "output_schema": {
      "quote": {
        "type": "string",
        "default": "把今天过好，就是对未来最好的投资。"
      },
      "author": {
        "type": "string",
        "default": "InkSight"
      }
    },
    "temperature": 0.85,
    "fallback": {
      "quote": "把今天过好，就是对未来最好的投资。",
      "author": "InkSight"
    },
    "fallback_pool": [
      {
        "quote": "把今天过好，就是对未来最好的投资。",
        "author": "InkSight"
      },
      {
        "quote": "你不需要更快，你需要更稳。",
        "author": "InkSight"
      },
      {
        "quote": "别等灵感，先把第一步做完。",
        "author": "InkSight"
      },
      {
        "quote": "把难事拆小，把小事做完。",
        "author": "InkSight"
      },
      {
        "quote": "减少选择，增加执行。",
        "author": "InkSight"
      }
    ]
  },
  "layout": {
    "status_bar": {
      "line_width": 1,
      "dashed": false
    },
    "layout_engine": "component_tree",
    "body_preset": "quote_focus_card",
    "preset_props": {
      "padding_x": 18,
      "justify": "center",
      "quote_inset_x": 20,
      "quote_field": "quote",
      "quote_font": "noto_serif_light",
      "quote_font_size": 20,
      "quote_max_lines": 4
    },
    "footer": {
      "label": "?????",
      "attribution_template": "— {author}"
    }
  },
  "layout_overrides": {
    "296x128": {
      "preset_props": {
        "padding_x": 8,
        "quote_inset_x": 8,
        "quote_font_size": 14,
        "quote_max_lines": 3
      },
      "footer": {
        "label": "?????",
        "attribution_template": "— {author}",
        "height": 18
      }
    },
    "648x480": {
      "preset_props": {
        "padding_x": 20,
        "quote_inset_x": 28,
        "quote_font_size": 22,
        "quote_max_lines": 4
      }
    },
"640x384": {
        "preset_props": {
            "padding_x": 20,
            "quote_inset_x": 28,
            "quote_font_size": 12,
            "quote_max_lines": 3
        }
    },
    "800x480": {
      "preset_props": {
        "padding_x": 28,
        "quote_inset_x": 48,
        "quote_font_size": 30,
        "quote_max_lines": 4
      }
    }
  }
}
